Best Weekend in AZ for our girl @jennifer_sumko Dress Launch with @dillards!! Every detail was 😍🤩. I met the MOST extraordinary new friends and even hit some great vintage shops! (Three cheers 🥂 to @christina__brian for being the ultimate hostess!!)

Spring Table styling.. because today is giving Spring feels ✨. I’m using 24 White (faux) cherry blossoms stems, Crystal Shell temple jar, Oslo Dish for candy, and the @alicelanehome candle… mmmmmm. Xo

HPMKT Day 2: Great conversation. Beautiful art. Delicious food. Lots of sitting in new and favorite things! Pinch me.. I feel like I’m dreaming!

HPMKT Day 3: The extraordinary @oly.studio, @centuryfurniture to see Thomas O’Brien, and Carrier & Co. @Palecek ..and so much more. 🤩 We love the beautiful lifestyles, textiles, styling.. fresh flowers.. it’s all so special!

HPMKT Day 4: Old Friends and New Friends paired with New Fabrics, New frames and great energy! One thing is for certain.. you can feel the passion that’s in the air, and the love of the game! Mad respect to all the vendors that came and showed off this week! It was a good one! 🤍

The New Phoenix Mirror(s) just dropped!! This collection of irregular antique rust mirrors was created to take the edge off most art installations, focus on soft form, and give an elevated found feel to your favorite spaces. 🤍

Tomorrow I learn from the best on how to properly pot my front porch!! I’ll take you along as I figure out how to do it! Also, can you believe everyone thought this wouldn’t fit in my car?? 🫠 (it nearly didn’t)
Saturday night at home. Happy Mothers Day to all you mommas, cheerleaders, nurturers, teachers, hustlers, lovers, and mentors! 🤍

My Mother, Polly Luekenga, is an earth angel. A mother to all who will let her love them. She’s like a compass, always knows the right thing to do or say in any difficult life altering moment. She’s an impossible example to follow, but I will forever be grateful I got to be the daughter, and she the mother. What a gift to be raised in her love. You can’t get a picture of her alone.. she’s a people magnet. So here are a few favorites over the years. And one in the middle of my own little family.. because being a Mom to my two little women is a privilege, I’ll forever be grateful I get to do!! 🤍🤍
So giddy for this new custom Chess Rug collection, choose your colors.. size, any size.. really truly, any difficult size, we will make it for you. Fun, huh?? ♟️ #chessrugs @alicelanehome

✨Treasure Hunt whilst in North Carolina this week.  @chelsea_on_green is #1 at the party!
My favorite was the tag 🏷️ that read, “From an important Palm Beach Collection”
Celebrating the great love of my life’s Birthday this weekend with dear friends, old stories, great food, matching costumes and Bruno Mars ✨
Right behind our house is a little Enchanted Forrest that ends in a park perfect for daily Lady walks. #spring2023
May 2023 | Putting this here as a Rolodex of what happened!! Life is but a dream 💭…

Fathers Day - Thankyou to the incredible Dad’s!  Grateful for their examples, tenderness, sense of humor, protection, nurturing, teachings, heart, and going the distance!! We love you, we honor you, we celebrate you!! Xoxo
Scenes for tomorrows photoshoot! @alicelanehome
Art Shopping @blue_print_store in Dallas today. What a treat! Highly recommend. @alicelaneinteriors
Ice cream break!

Everyone should be so lucky to try on sunnies with Sue @hallahall!! Enjoy ✨😎
Summer Nights. Long walks with Jane. 4 weeks left before she moves away to college. Drinking in each moment with her.
Celebrating @barbie week with @alicelaneinteriors and the completion of our own version of The Barbie Dream house! 💓🍿
Don’t forget to cut those hydrangeas and enjoy them inside, before the season is gone. 🍃

Big thanks to @domojosh & @marinabjames!! 💫
Fall in 🍁UTAH! Sardine Canyon was really showing off this evening!! Next weekend is supposed to be peak colors. Get outside 😍 it’s incredible !!

It was a great evening meeting so many at The Dear Alice Live Event @alicelanehome!! Thankyou all who came, said hello, for tuning into the podcast over the past 4 years!! It means the world! We finally got to show you what we are trying to describe each week in words. ❤️ #dearalicepodcast #interiordesign
New J.Bennett Iris Mirror in my entry adds the depth I was missing, and gave an unexpected shape making me instantly feel more Chic! ✨@alicelanehome #irisgrandmirror 🪞

@hpmkt Day 1: Drank from the firehouse that is Market.. Today we saw Beautiful creative talented friends, New collections for Spring, Color, Gorgeous lifestyles, New showrooms, Incredible space-planning , new silhouettes for outdoor furniture!! Can’t wait till all if this is available! ✨ @alicelanehome @alicelaneinteriors

Market Day 2: The vintage shops are an ever inspiring well of creativity. And hitting some new up and coming temporary booths.. to see what’s new. Old vs. New ever the question when choosing great design! @alicelaneinteriors @alicelanehome

Fall cocktail table styling. Keep it effortless, and make it personal. I’m using a few favorites from the j.Bennett collection. ‘JESS20’ gets you 20% off everything in the  collection thru 10/22. @alicelanehome

Fall #Hpmkt was giving us Spring ‘24. Color was a theme, my eyes kept seeing golden, maize, yellow, hues.. but all the candy 🍬 notes were there showing off! Can’t wait!! 👏🏼👏🏼 Here are a few of my faves..
@alicelanehome @alicelaneinteriors
Fourteen…turns out 14 is the magic number of long pine branches needed to fill the large crystal shell jar! In case you were curious too! 🌲✨ #longpine&pineconebranch #opalshelljar @alicelanehome

The Holiday Collection is now available online @alicelanehome.. I couldn’t help myself, I had to play with the new goodies at home this weekend. On my mantle are: 2 Long needle pine garlands and 6 cypress sprays layered in making up the foundation. I added 5 crystal obelisks, and 3 crystal candlesticks. The silver and gold beaded ⚪️🟡 garlands available in store.. and those candy 🍬 ornaments too!
The Penny lamp is now available in solid alabaster!! I’m giddy.. I can’t decide where it should live at my house.. the Living room, or my Bathroom? @alicelanehome

Weekends are for little luxuries like fresh stems.  No matter what I bring home.. the Jessica Vase from @theclaymaven is my favorite! Perfect scale, great color/texture.. perfect  in every room in my house!

The Curiosity Collection GOLD BAR is fun to style with, and a great conversation piece! So excited to pair with a love note this season, and gift my friends letting them know all the ways I think they are Golden ✨. @alicelanehome

The Curiosity Collection WISHBONE is a little added luck, or wish for that friend that needs extra hope 💫 this season.. or anytime. I’m hanging one of these on my girls stockings this year! Who doesn’t need luck on their side? @alicelanehome  #wishbone

Here’s to 2023, the great friends, the growth, the love, the trials.. I’m here for it!! It’s all shaping and defining what’s happening inside me. Hopefully making me better equipped for 2024. Life is sweeter 🍬 with friends!! #Grateful ❤️ #Novembering

The clawfoot candle dish got a make-over just in time for gifting! And we are bringing you a new larger size, The clawfoot tray! Showing you the differences between the old and new here. ✨@alicelanehome #thecuriositycollection

Depeche Mode has still got it! 💫 Great Show! 
Thanks for the fun @domojosh & @marinabjames

Is there a better week in the whole year?? The delicious warm gratitude of Thanksgiving.. and that Christmas anticipation high! Happy Holidays y’all! Feel it all 💓✨.. it’s as close to magic as it gets!  Xo
